fuel_table_lookup_front.description: The length of the fuel pulse on the front cylinder as dictated by the fuel table before correction

fuel_table_lookup_rear.description: The length of the fuel pulse on the rear cylinder as dictated by the fuel table before correction

fuel_pulse_front.description: The length of the fuel pulse on the front cylinder

fuel_pulse_rear.description: The length of the fuel pulse on the rear cylinder

fuel_correction_battery.description: Corrects the fuel pulse length based on the voltage of the battery

fuel_correction_engine_temperature.description: Corrects the fuel pulse length based on the engine temperature

fuel_correction_ambient_temperature.description: Corrects the fuel pulse length based on the ambient air temperature

fuel_correction_engine_acceleration.description: Corrects the fuel pulse length based on the acceleration of the engine RPM

fuel_correction_engine_deceleration.description: Corrects the fuel pulse length based on the deceleration of the engine RPM

fuel_correction_wide_open_throttle.description: Corrects the fuel pulse length when the throttle is fully open

fuel_correction_idle.description: Corrects the fuel pulse length when the engine is at idle

fuel_correction_learned_rear.description: Corrects the fuel pulse length based on learning from the Oxygen sensor. Applies to the rear cylinder or both cylinders on bikes with only one oxygen sensor.

estimated_mixture_rear.description: The ECM's best guess at the current fuel/air mixture (percent lean or rich). Applies to the rear cylinder or both cylinders on bikes with only one oxygen sensor.

FP_PWM_Duty.description: Fuel Pressure PWM duty cycle (KFPC_Config enabled)

vehicle_speed_kph.description: Vehicle speed in KPH (enable in KVS_Config)

manifold_air_pressure_front.description: Air Pressure in the front intake manifold

manifold_air_pressure_rear.description: Air Pressure in the rear intake manifold

fuel_correction_learned_front.description: Corrects the fuel pulse length in the front cylinder based on learning from the oxygen sensor.

estimated_mixture_front.description: The ECM's best guess at the current fuel/air mixture (percent lean or rich) in the front cylinder.

oxygen_sensor_reading_rear.description: Rear Air/Fuel Ratio (0-5V=10-20AFR). Only works when wide-band oxygen sensors are connected.
